        .wolf-item
          .wolf-item-inner
            .figcaption
              p When Kara Walker's Sugar Baby took over the Domino Sugar Factory, I was asked to photograph it prior to the opening in order to create a interactive 3D rendering of the work. Instagram photos with the hashtag #KaraWalkerDomino then built upon the base that I had established. I also shot the promotional photos for the project.

        .wolf-item
          .wolf-item-inner
            .wolf-media.portfolio-media
              iframe(src='https://player.vimeo.com/video/100137078?autoplay=1&loop=1&color=79c7c1&title=0&byline=0', width='500', height='281', frameborder='0', webkitallowfullscreen='', mozallowfullscreen='', allowfullscreen='')
