                img(src='img/ct/ct_03.png', alt='SEO NAME')
        .wolf-item.is-caption--left
          .wolf-item-inner
            .wolf-media.portfolio-media
              .figcaption
                p When Nick Cave's transformed Grand Central Terminal’s Vanderbilt Hall with a herd of thirty colorful life-size horses for the show HEARD•NY, Creative Time asked Makeable to create a social media aggregator for posts tagged #IHEARDNY from Facebook, Twitter, Vine, Instagram, and Foursquare. Following the show, I developed an interactive thank you piece showing a selection of posts curated by the artist himself. The social media platform's APIs were used to pull the posts into SVG letters where visitors could explore them.

